32\u0430\u043b \u041a\u0443\u0431\u043e\u043a \u0422\u0443\u0440\u043a\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0430 \u043f\u043e \u0444\u0443\u0442\u0431\u043e\u043b\u0443]</ref>\n\n===Domestic===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Season\n! colspan=\"9\" | League\n! rowspan=\"2\" | [[Turkmenistan Cup]]\n! colspan=\"2\" | Top goalscorer\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Manager\n|-\n! Div.\n! Pos.\n! Pl.\n! W\n! D\n! L\n! GS\n! GA\n! P\n! Name\n! League\n|-\n|align=center|[[2015 \u00ddokary Liga|2015]]\n|align=center|1st\n|align=center|'''4'''\n|align=center|36\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|10\n|align=center|10\n|align=center|59\n|align=center|36\n|align=center|'''58'''\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:silver;\"|'''[[2015 Turkmenistan Cup|Runner-Up]]'''\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center|{{flagicon|Turkmenistan}} [[Amanmyrat Meredow]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2016 \u00ddokary Liga|2016]]\n|align=center|1st\n|align=center|'''8'''\n|align=center|36\n|align=center|8\n|align=center|8\n|align=center|20\n|align=center|20\n|align=center|38\n|align=center|'''32'''\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|-\n|align=center|[[2019 \u00ddokary Liga|2019]]\n|align=center|1st\n|align=center|'''3'''\n|align=center|28\n|align=center|15\n|align=center|7\n|align=center|6\n|align=center|25\n|align=center|42\n|align=center|'''42'''\n|align=center| Quarter-finals\n|align=center| [[Kerim Hojaberdi\u00fdew]]\n|align=center| 7\n|align=center|{{flagicon|Turkmenistan}} [[Aleksandr Klimenko (footballer)|Aleksandr Klimenko]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n* '''[[Turkmenistan League]]: 1'''\n** Winner: 2002\n* '''[[Turkmenistan Cup]]: 1'''\n** Winner: 2007\n** Runner-up(2): 2002, [[2015 Turkmenistan Cup|2015]]\n* '''[[Turkmenistan Super Cup]]:'''\n** Runner-up: 2007\n\n\n==Squad==\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=2 |nat=TKM|name=[[Begen\u00e7 Gyly\u00e7ny\u00fdazow]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=3 |nat=TKM|name=[[\u00ddunus Orazm\u00e4