irus (region)|Epirus]] - \u00c9piro\n*[[Euboea]] - Eubeia\n*[[Ionian Islands]] - Ilhas J\u00f3nicas\n*[[Macedonia (Greece)|Macedonia]] - Maced\u00f3nia (PT), Maced\u00f4nia (BR)\n*[[Marathon, Greece|Marathon]] - Maratona\n*[[Naupactus]] - Lepanto\n*[[Rhodes]] - Rodes\n*[[Peloponnese]] - Peloponeso\n*[[Piraeus]] - Pireu\n*[[Samothrace]] - Samotr\u00e1cia\n*[[Sparta]] - Esparta\n*[[Thebes, Greece|Thebes]] - Tebas\n*[[Thessaloniki]] - Sal\u00f3nica/Tessal\u00f3nica (PT), Sal\u00f4nica/Tessal\u00f4nica (BR)\n*[[Thessaly]] - Tess\u00e1lia\n*[[Thrace]] - Tr\u00e1cia\n*[[Zakynthos]] - Zaquintos\n\n==Hungary - Hungria==\n\n*[[Budapest]] - Budapeste\n\n==Ireland - Irlanda==\n\n*[[Dublin]] - Dublim\n\n==Italy - It\u00e1lia==\n\n*[[Arezzo]] - Ar\u00e9cio (archaic)\n*[[Assisi]] - Assis\n*[[Baragiano]] - Baraj\u00e3o (PT, very rare)\n*[[Bologna]] - Bolonha\n*[[Calabria]] - Cal\u00e1bria\n*[[Cagliari]] - C\u00e1lhari (PT)\n*[[Campania]] - Camp\u00e2nia\n*[[Florence]] - Floren\u00e7a\n*[[Genoa]] - G\u00e9nova (PT), G\u00eanova (BR)\n*[[Lazio]] - L\u00e1cio (rare)\n*[[Liguria]] - Lig\u00faria\n*[[Lombardy]] - Lombardia\n*[[Mantua]] (''Mantova'') - M\u00e2ntua\n*[[Milan]] (''Milano'') - Mil\u00e3o\n*[[Naples]] (''Napoli'') - N\u00e1poles\n*[[Padua]] (''Padova'') - P\u00e1dua\n*[[Piacenza]] - Plas\u00eancia (PT)\n*[[Piedmont]] - Piemonte\n*[[Rome]] - Roma\n*[[Sardinia]] - Sardenha\n*[[Sicily]] - Sic\u00edlia\n*[[Tiber]] - Tibre\n*[[Turin]] (''Torino'') - Turim\n*[[Tuscany]] - Toscana\n*[[Venice]] - Veneza\n*[[Mount Vesuvius|Vesuvius]] - Ves\u00favio\n\n==Latvia - Let\u00f3nia (PT), Let\u00f4nia (BR)==\n\n*[[Courland]] - Curl\u00e2ndia (PT, archaic)\n*[[Latgale]] - Lateg\u00e1lia, Latg\u00e1lia, Leteg\u00e1lia, Letg\u00e1lia (PT, all archaic)\n*[[Zemgale]] - Semigola, Semig\u00e1lia (PT, both archaic)\n\n==Lithuania - Litu\u00e2nia==\n\n*[[Klaip\u0117da]] - Memel, Memelburgo (PT, both archaic)\n*[[Lithuania Minor]] - Litu\u00e2nia Menor\n*[[Samogitia]] - Samog\u00edcia (archaic)\n*[[V