l\u00e1quia\n\n==Russia - R\u00fassia==\n\n*[[Adygea]] - Adigu\u00e9sia (rare), Adigeia (rare)\n*[[Arkhangelsk]] - Arcangel (rare)\n*[[Bashkortostan]] - Bascortost\u00e3o (rare)\n*[[Chechnya]] - Tchetch\u00e9nia/Chech\u00e9nia (PT), Tchetch\u00eania/Chech\u00eania (BR)\n*[[Dagestan]] - Daguest\u00e3o\n*[[Ingushetia]] - Inguch\u00e9tia (rare)\n*[[Kabardino-Balkaria]] - Cab\u00e1rdia-Balc\u00e1ria (rare)\n*[[Kaliningrad]] - Kaliningrado\n*[[Kalmykia]] - Calm\u00faquia (rare)\n*[[Karachay-Cherkessia]] - Carachai-Circ\u00e1ssia (rare)\n*[[Karelia]] - Car\u00e9lia\n*[[Kazan]] - Caz\u00e3\n*''formerly'' [[Leningrad]] - Leninegrado (PT), Leningrado (BR)\n*[[Mordovia]] - Mord\u00f3via\n*[[Moscow|Moskva]] - Moscovo (PT), Moscou (BR)\n*[[Orenburg]] - Oremburgo (rare)\n*[[Ossetia]] - Oss\u00e9tia\n*''formerly'' [[Petrograd]] - Petrogrado\n*[[Saint Petersburg]] - S\u00e3o Petersburgo, Sampetersburgo (very rare)\n*[[Qashliq|Sibir]] - Sib\u00e9ria\n*''formerly'' [[Stalingrad]] - Estalinegrado (PT), Stalingrado (BR)\n*[[Tatarstan]] - Tatarist\u00e3o\n*[[Udmurtia]] - Udm\u00fartia\n*[[Volgograd]] - Volgogrado\n*[[Yekaterinburg]] - Ecaterimburgo\n\n==Serbia - S\u00e9rvia==\n\n*[[Belgrade]] - Belgrado\n**[[Novi Beograd]] - Nova Belgrado\n*[[Banat]] - Banato\n*[[Dunav]] - Dan\u00fabio\n*[[Smederevo]] - Sem\u00eandria (archaic)\n*[[Vojvodina]] - Voivodina\n\n==Slovakia - Eslov\u00e1quia==\n\n\n==Slovenia - Eslov\u00e9nia (PT), Eslov\u00eania (BR)==\n\n*[[Idrija]] - \u00cddria\n*[[Koper]] - Capod\u00edstria\n*[[Ljubljana]] - Liubliana\n*[[Lucija]] - Luc\u00eda\n*[[Maribor]] - Marburgo (archaic)\n\n==Spain - Espanha==\n\n*[[A Coru\u00f1a|A Coru\u00f1a - La Coru\u00f1a]] - (A) Corunha\n*[[Almer\u00eda]] - Almeria\n*[[Andalusia]] - Andaluzia\n*[[Arag\u00f3n]] - Arag\u00e3o\n*[[Asturias]] - Ast\u00farias\n*[[Balearic Islands]] - Ilhas Baleares\n*[[Bilbao]] - Bilbau (PT)\n*[[Biscay]] - Biscaia\n*[[C\u00e1diz]] - C\u00e1dis (PT)\n*[[Canary Islands]] - Ilhas Can\u00e1rias\n*[[Cantabria]] - Can