ruges\n*[[Brussels]] - Bruxelas\n*[[Ghent]] - Gante\n*[[Leuven]] - Lovaina\n*[[Meuse (river)|Maas]] - Mosa (PT)\n*[[Scheldt]] - Escalda\n*[[Flanders]] - Flandres\n*[[Wallonia]] - Val\u00f3nia (PT), Val\u00f4nia (BR)\n\n==Bosnia and Herzegovina - B\u00f3snia e Herzegovina==\n\n*[[Sarajevo]] - Saraievo\n\n==Bulgaria - Bulg\u00e1ria==\n\n*[[Sofia]] - S\u00f3fia\n\n==Croatia - Cro\u00e1cia==\n\n*[[Zagreb]] - Zagrebe\n\n==Cyprus - Chipre==\n\n*[[Limassol|Lemesos/Limasol]] - Limassol\n*[[Nicosia]] - Nic\u00f3sia\n*[[Paphos]] - Pafos\n\n==Czech Republic/Czechia - Rep\u00fablica Checa(PT)/Tcheca(BR), Ch\u00e9quia (PT), Tch\u00e9quia (BR)==\n\n*[[Brno]] - Brum, Bruno (both rare)\n*[[Prague]] - Praga\n*[[Plze\u0148]] - Pilsen, Pilzem (rare)\n*[[Sudetes]] - Sudetas (PT), Sudetos (BR)\n\n==Denmark - Dinamarca==\n\n*[[Frisia|Frisland]] - Fr\u00edsia\n*[[Faroe Islands]] - Ilhas F\u00e9roe, Ilhas Faro\u00e9\n*[[Greenland]] - Gronel\u00e2ndia (PT), Groenl\u00e2ndia (BR)\n*[[Jylland]] - Jutl\u00e2ndia\n*[[Copenhagen]] - Copenhaga (PT), Copenhague (BR)\n\n==Estonia - Est\u00f3nia (PT), Est\u00f4nia (BR)==\n\n*[[Tallinn]] - Talim\n\n==Finland - Finl\u00e2ndia==\n\n*[[Aaland]] - Alanda (PT)\n*[[Helsinki]] - Hels\u00ednquia (PT), Helsinque (BR)\n*[[Lapland (Finland)|Lapland]] - Lap\u00f3nia (PT), Lap\u00f4nia (BR)\n\n==France - Fran\u00e7a==\n\n*[[Alsace]] - Als\u00e1cia\n*[[Aquitaine]] - Aquit\u00e2nia\n*[[Auvergne (region)|Auvergne]] - Auv\u00e9rnia\n*[[Avignon]] - Avinh\u00e3o\n*[[Bayonne]] - Baiona\n*[[Bordeaux]] - Bord\u00e9us (PT, rare in Brazil)\n*[[Burgundy (region)|Burgundy]] - Borgonha\n*[[Brittany]] - Bretanha\n*[[Carcassonne]] - Carcassona\n*[[Champagne, France|Champagne]] - Champanhe\n*[[Corsica]] - C\u00f3rsega\n*[[Franche-Comt\u00e9]] - Franco-Condado\n*[[Gascony]] - Gasconha\n*[[Lorraine (region)|Lorraine]] - Lorena\n*[[Lyon]] - Li\u00e3o (PT, archaic)\n*[[Marseille]] - Marselha\n*[[Massif Central]] - Maci\u00e7o Central\n*[[Meuse (river)|Meuse]] - Mosa\n*[[Monaco]] - M\