art]] - Estugarda (PT, archaic in Brazil)\n*[[Thuringia]] - Tur\u00edngia\n*[[T\u00fcbingen]] - Tubinga (PT)\n*[[Westfalen]] (Westphalia) - Vestef\u00e1lia (PT), Vestf\u00e1lia (BR)\n*[[W\u00fcrttemberg]] - Vurtemberga (PT)\n*[[W\u00fcrzburg]] - Vurzburgo (archaic)\n\n==Greece - Gr\u00e9cia==\n\n*[[Athens]] - Atenas\n*[[Attica]] - \u00c1tica\n*[[Boeotia]] - Be\u00f3cia\n*[[Cephalonia]] - Cefal\u00f3nia (PT), Cefal\u00f4nia (BR) (both rare)\n*[[Corfu]] - Corfu\n*[[Corinth]] - Corinto\n*[[Crete]] - Creta\n*[[Cyclades]] - C\u00edclades\n*[[Dodecanese]] - Dodecaniso\n*[[Epirus (region)|Epirus]] - \u00c9piro\n*[[Euboea]] - Eubeia\n*[[Ionian Islands]] - Ilhas J\u00f3nicas\n*[[Macedonia (Greece)|Macedonia]] - Maced\u00f3nia (PT), Maced\u00f4nia (BR)\n*[[Marathon, Greece|Marathon]] - Maratona\n*[[Naupactus]] - Lepanto\n*[[Rhodes]] - Rodes\n*[[Peloponnese]] - Peloponeso\n*[[Piraeus]] - Pireu\n*[[Samothrace]] - Samotr\u00e1cia\n*[[Sparta]] - Esparta\n*[[Thebes, Greece|Thebes]] - Tebas\n*[[Thessaloniki]] - Sal\u00f3nica/Tessal\u00f3nica (PT), Sal\u00f4nica/Tessal\u00f4nica (BR)\n*[[Thessaly]] - Tess\u00e1lia\n*[[Thrace]] - Tr\u00e1cia\n*[[Zakynthos]] - Zaquintos\n\n==Hungary - Hungria==\n\n*[[Budapest]] - Budapeste\n\n==Ireland - Irlanda==\n\n*[[Dublin]] - Dublim\n\n==Italy - It\u00e1lia==\n\n*[[Arezzo]] - Ar\u00e9cio (archaic)\n*[[Assisi]] - Assis\n*[[Baragiano]] - Baraj\u00e3o (PT, very rare)\n*[[Bologna]] - Bolonha\n*[[Calabria]] - Cal\u00e1bria\n*[[Cagliari]] - C\u00e1lhari (PT)\n*[[Campania]] - Camp\u00e2nia\n*[[Florence]] - Floren\u00e7a\n*[[Genoa]] - G\u00e9nova (PT), G\u00eanova (BR)\n*[[Lazio]] - L\u00e1cio (rare)\n*[[Liguria]] - Lig\u00faria\n*[[Lombardy]] - Lombardia\n*[[Mantua]] (''Mantova'') - M\u00e2ntua\n*[[Milan]] (''Milano'') - Mil\u00e3o\n*[[Naples]] (''Napoli'') - N\u00e1poles\n*[[Padua]] (''Padova'') - P\u00e1dua\n*[[Piacenza]] - Plas\u00eancia (PT)\n*[[Piedmont]] - Piemonte\n*[[Rome]] - Roma\n*[[Sardinia]] - Sardenha\n*[[Sicily]] - Sic\u00edlia\n*[[Tiber]]